name: A Car Going Somewhere
description:
This piece was inspired by one of ESAE’s song, “A Car Going Nowhere.

As Im living my 20s there are so many things that I worry about. I dont even know what’s the purpose of life and why I keep living, but I cant just take away my life either. So, I decided to just keep going and enjoy the ride.

And if anyone asked where Im going, tbh, I have no idea. Somewhere, Im going somewhere.
